data.description: Absolutely CHARMING 1949 Built Block 3 OVERSIZED Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, MASSIVE FLORIDA ROOM PLUS Utility Workshop within a few blocks of DOWNTOWN HISTORIC District. BRAND NEW METAL ROOF MAY 2023! With over 2050 total Square Footage this GEM will not disappoint! Vibrant low maintenance curb appeal greets you into the oversized COVERED CARPORT with extended concrete driveway shared with the adorable Front Porch to enjoy relaxing days/nights. Two Front entrances; one with a Glass Storm Door lands you into the Tiled Foyer for convenient access to the Centrally located Kitchen and/or Master En-Suite.  TRIPLE SPLIT FLOOR PLAN divided by the quaint Kitchen featuring 2 designer light fixtures, NEWER GAS RANGE (2 years new) SOARING FLOOR TO CEILING WOOD CABINENTRY, Reverse Osmosis Water System, NEWER Stainless Steel Frigidaire Side X Side Refrigerator (2 years new) Split Stainless Steel sink, Tiled Countertops, Neutral Deco Tile Flooring, Plenty of Natural Sunlight, Undercabinet lighting, Dinette seating area with plenty of counter space! This Primary En-Suite IS OVERSIZED allowing for King Suite or additional seating area with a HUGE WALK-IN closet complete with Shelving, En-Suite Bathroom with Walk-in Shower, distinguished wood flooring, HEAT LAMP, Ample Vanity Space and Newer Commode. Second Quarter of Home entails TWO MAGNIFICANTLY SIZED GUEST BEDROOMS with MASSIVE WALK-IN CLOSETS (9x6 & 5x7). Both rooms offer Ceiling Fans, Window Treatments/Blinds/Curtains/Rods divided by unique designated Linen Closet nestled in the Hallway shared with guest Bathroom equipped with TUB/SHOWER combination, Vanity with Storage, Tile Flooring complete with Pfister Hardware. Third Quarter is a well-appointed DINING/EXTENDED PANTRY/STORAGE/INDOOR LAUNDRY CLOSET, SO MANY OPTIONS FOR THIS WINDOWED WALL shared with French Door leading to the 28 x 8 FLORIDA ROOM with designated A/C and HEAT. Enjoy PANORAMIC Views of the PRIVATE, FULLY FENCED Rear and Side Yard.  UTILITY SHED with Electric, Shelving PLUS A FULLY FUNCTIONAL OPENAIR WORKSHOP complete with Electricity, COVERED-EXPOSED overhead open Truss for storage, Sink, workbench and EXTENDED COVERED PORCH. ENOUGH ROOM FOR A POOL or utilize the double gate side entrance to park your Boat or RV! Fenced Chicken run, rain gutters, multiple designated window air conditioners, CENTRAL A/C fully re-furbished September 2023, WASHER/TWO (2) Dryers, pre-plumbed for water softener, furnishings and CONVENIENT location to local Ice Cream shops, Post Office, Churches, DOWNTOWN and HISTORIC DISTRICT, Movie Theatre, Hospital, High School, Fire Department are all WITHIN BLOCKS of your new home! NO HOA. Confirm your showing today, this home will NOT last!
